Clearcase issue:

cleartool: Error: Operation "view_ws_is_ws_view" failed: view storage directory or control files unavailable --

Solution:
  - end the view first: clearcase endview -server <view_name>
  - go to view directory: cd /ws/ytse-sjc/ytse-<view_name>
    Can also find view server access path using: clearcase lsview -l <view_name>
  - remove the file ".pid"

